OL,3,COffering work experience 'too time
OL,4,Cconsuming', some businesses claim
OL,6,FTwo in five (41%) businesses that do
OL,7,Fnot offer work experience to school
OL,8,Fpupils say it is too time consuming, a
OL,9,Fsurvey has found.
OL,11,FA third of senior business leaders
OL,12,Fsurveyed by The Careers & Enterprise
OL,13,FCompany (CEC) not offering work
OL,14,Fexperience also said they do not have
OL,15,Fthe staff capacity to supervise work
OL,16,Fexperience (33%), or they lack
OL,17,Fsuitable tasks for young people (34%).
OL,19,FOf 750 business leaders surveyed in
OL,20,Ftotal, just over half (52%) said they
OL,21,Fcurrently offer work experience.
