OL,3,COffering work experience 'too time
OL,4,Cconsuming', some businesses claim
OL,6,FMore than half (58%) said the
OL,7,Ftraditional two-week work experience
OL,8,Fblock is too time consuming.
OL,10,FThis comes after the Government's post-
OL,11,F16 education and skills white paper
OL,12,Fpromised to deliver at least two weeks
OL,13,Fof work experience for all secondary
OL,14,Fschool students, with a goal of
OL,15,Fsplitting this into at least one
OL,16,Fweek's worth of experience in years
OL,17,Fseven to nine, and the other in years
OL,18,F10 to 11.
