OL,6,FLast week the Office for National
OL,7,FStatistics said the number of young
OL,8,Fpeople not in employment, education or
OL,9,Ftraining (Neet) remained close to a
OL,10,Fmillion from July to September at
OL,11,F946,000.
OL,13,F"Work experience is absolutely
OL,14,Ffundamental to ensuring that young
OL,15,Fpeople have that line of sight to
OL,16,Fwhere they need to get to," Skills
OL,17,FEngland deputy chief executive officer
OL,18,FGemma Marsh told a CEC event last week.
