OL,3,COffering work experience 'too time
OL,4,Cconsuming', some businesses claim
OL,6,FMore than two in three (68%) of
OL,7,Fbusinesses surveyed by CEC said entry-
OL,8,Flevel candidates are underprepared for
OL,9,Fthe world of work.
OL,11,FThree quarters (75%) of businesses
OL,12,Falso said making it easier to work
OL,13,Fwith schools would make them more
OL,14,Flikely to offer work experience.
OL,16,FCEC is advocating for short, flexible
OL,17,Fwork experience placements to make up
OL,18,Fthe weeks' worth of experience in both
OL,19,Fyears seven to nine and years 10 to 11.
