OL,6,FThese should prioritise young people
OL,7,Fwho are missing out and provide
OL,8,Ftargeted support, and start early to
OL,9,Fallow students to access different
OL,10,Findustries.
OL,12,F"This is very much a new attempt to
OL,13,Fbreak away from two-week block work
OL,14,Fexperiences that for too long been
OL,15,Ffound to be inflexible, impractical,
OL,16,Fand out of reach for many students and
OL,17,Femployers," said Baroness Nicky
OL,18,FMorgan, former Conservative education
OL,19,Fsecretary and CEC chairwoman, speaking
OL,20,Fat CEC's event on Friday.
