OL,3,COffering work experience 'too time
OL,4,Cconsuming', some businesses claim
OL,6,FCEC is calling on schools and
OL,7,Femployers to sign up to its new
OL,8,Fapproach to work experience to help
OL,9,Fgive young people more choice.
OL,11,FEllis Potter, head of apprenticeships
OL,12,Fand careers at The Priory Federation
OL,13,Fof Academies Trust, said: "We can only
OL,14,Fdeliver this if more employers get
OL,15,Finvolved.
OL,17,F"When businesses open their doors, our
OL,18,Fstudents gain a clearer sense of what
OL,19,Fwork really looks like and leave
OL,20,Fschool even more prepared for their
OL,21,Ffuture pathways."
